subtitleNullable: Pro-Eating Disorder (pro-ana) material vs Pro-Recovery material
descriptionNullable:
### Context

In my Abnormal Psychology class, I learned about how pro-anorexia/pro-eating disorder material online can be harmful, so I decided to make a dataset, in hopes that it would help someone with the necessary skills to make a model that might end up helping someone some day. 


### Content

This dataset contains the same data in several formats. There is the combined data as both a .csv and .xls, and the separated data as .xls files. The first column contains an ID that corresponds to the order the sentences were in originally. The second column is the id (0 for pro-recovery, 1 for pro-ana), and the third row is a sentence (defined by the character ".")
